data.description: MOVE IN READY, NEWLY PAINTED, AND NEWLY CARPETED 4 bedroom/2.5 bathroom home in the VERY SOUGHT AFTER TWIN LAKES SUBDIVISION in Hoschton has so much for so many people!  The flooring on the main level is stunning, there is new carpet upstairs, and the interior has been freshly painted!  There is a BIG, OPEN EAT IN KITCHEN with GRANITE COUNTER TOPS, a GRANITE TOP ISLAND, a HUGE WALK IN PANTRY, GREY CABINETRY, a BIG BREAKFAST AREA, and more! The SPACIOUS FAMILY ROOM is totally OPEN FROM THE KITCHEN!  A door leads to the COVERED BACK PATIO which overlooks the HUGE BACK YARD!!!  There is also a lovely DINING ROOM ON THE MAIN LEVEL!!!  Upstairs is the HUGE MASTER SUITE featuring a BIG WALK IN CLOSET, A TREY CEILING, and more! The MASTER BATH has a SEPARATE TUB AND SHOWER along with DUAL VANITIES!!!  All of the bedrooms upstairs offer plenty of space!  For your convenience, the LAUNDRY ROOM is located NEAR ALL OF THE BEDROOMS UPSTAIRS!  Twin Lakes is a thriving Swim Community that is still growing and prospering!!!  Come and see this lovely home today!!!
